    <item>
      <title>巴克莱誓言在改革中向投资者返还 100 亿英镑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-20/barclays-aims-to-cut-costs-by-2-billion-in-bid-to-boost-returns</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴克莱银行表示，将继续大力削减成本，重组其报告结构，并在未来几年向股东返还至少 100 亿英镑，结束数月来对这家欧洲最大投资银行之一未来方向的猜测。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-20/barclays-aims-to-cut-costs-by-2-billion-in-bid-to-boost-returns</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 20 Feb 2024 07:14:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国股市监管机构罕见采取行动，誓言听取市场批评以避免 5 万亿美元暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-20/china-stock-watchdog-vows-to-heed-market-calls-even-criticism</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国证券监管机构表示，将听取市场参与者的所有建议甚至批评，并及时解决他们的担忧，这一罕见的举动突显了其支撑中国8.6万亿美元股市的决心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-20/china-stock-watchdog-vows-to-heed-market-calls-even-criticism</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 20 Feb 2024 01:59:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>股市、美国期货因中国担忧而回落：市场总结</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-19/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管企业消息和财报提供了一些亮点，但由于对中国经济的持续担忧令全球市场承压，欧洲股市和美国股指期货下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-19/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 22:58:37 GMT</pubDate>
